As a student I need a place to upload my project files so that Studio lectururs may track my progress.
As a Studio lecturer I want to manage student's and their work efficiently so that I all of my notes are in one place.
As a lecturer I want to be able to display students information so that I can tell who is who and what class they belong to.
As a lecturer I want to be able to see a list of each students in each clasroom so that I am able to differentiate each classes work.
As a lecturer I need to be able to access students' completed work so that I may mark and create notes for.
As a lecturer I want to provide a secure platform for other lecturers to monitor their own classes work.
As a lecturer I want to be able to know when a student moves to the next studio class upon swapping of semesters so i have fresh classes every swap.

